snippet.title: Cute ANNOYING ANIMALS WAKING UP OWNERS - Bet you'll LAUGH ALL DAY LONG
snippet.description:
Cute funny pets trying to wake up their owners! So ridiculous, funny and cute! Cats and dogs are the best. They make us laugh all the time, even when they annoy us! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
